General.Name: Gold Recycle Corp
General.Description: The Fight Zone, Inc. develops and markets global positioning system (GPS) stereo camera products for applications in insurance, emergency management, and first response markets. The company was formerly known as GeoScopix, Inc. and changed its name to The Fight Zone, Inc. in October 2006. The company was founded in 1995 and is based in Addison, Texas.
